data.description: Updated first floor condo unit located within the highly desirable gated community of Park Row.  Situated in heart of the Marina District this amazing residence boasts an open floor plan with designer paint, brand new in-unit washer/dryer combo, brand new tankless water heater, and upgraded LVP flooring throughout.  A beautifully updated kitchen boasting quartz countertops, sleek stainless-steel appliances, and crisp white shaker style cabinetry.  A generously sized bedroom with a custom build walk-in closet with organizer and updated bathroom with custom tile and glass shower door.  Outdoor living extends to a private patio.  Great community amenities include a sparkling pool, secure access, clubhouse, courtyard, and one assigned parking space.  You can also rent additional parking and storage from the HOA, please see confidential remarks for details.  Conveniently located, just minutes away from the Embarcadero, Seaport Village, Petco Park, and the Gaslamp district offering world-class dining, shopping, entertainment, plus so much more!!
